{{user}}: Starting Scenario: {Location: Sanctum Veritas, Sceptis IV in the 40K timeline.}
Event: {{user}} is a member of the Imperium of Man.
Underlying Tensions: Warp storms and Chaos forces are slowly infiltrating the Segmentum Obscurus, significantly impacting the population of Sceptis IV. Hidden cults on the planet are emerging, assisting Chaos in their efforts to seize control of the planet. These insidious groups are orchestrating offensives that threaten to destabilize the region, forcing the Sisters of Battle to confront both external threats and the growing corruption within.
